# VHS demo tape for univiz

# Settings
Output univiz-demo.gif
Output univiz-demo.svg
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 40
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Require univiz

# Demo
Type "# Univiz - utf8 string analyzer"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "univiz"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type 'univiz "Hello 👋"'
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type 'univiz "café 😀🎉"'
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 2s